    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a charset-normalizer Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>charset-normalizer</application> library helps reading text
from an unknown character encoding.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

      <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Informao do Pacote</bridgehead>
      <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
